# Regression test fixtures: post-install snapshots under expected/ are golden
# files committed to the repo. The patterns above match `.agents/` etc.
# anywhere in the tree, so we re-include them for the regression-case dirs.
!tests/regression/cases/*/expected/.agents/
!tests/regression/cases/*/expected/.claude/
!tests/regression/cases/*/expected/.opencode/
!tests/regression/cases/*/expected/.cursor/
